# Admin Interface Patterns

## Authentication
- Use NextAuth.js session management
- Protect admin routes with middleware
- Redirect unauthenticated users to login
- Use server-side session checks

## Admin Layout
- Use [AdminSidebar.tsx](mdc:src/components/admin/AdminSidebar.tsx) for navigation
- Implement responsive mobile navigation
- Show current page in sidebar
- Use consistent admin styling

## CRUD Operations
- Use modal forms for create/edit operations
- Implement confirmation dialogs for deletions
- Show loading states during operations
- Use toast notifications for feedback

## Form Patterns
- Use controlled components with useState
- Implement proper validation
- Handle cascading dropdowns (ConsoleType â†’ Console)
- Show image previews when URLs are provided
- Use proper form submission with loading states

## Table Patterns
- Use responsive table layouts
- Implement search and filtering
- Show action buttons (Edit, Delete)
- Use confirmation modals for destructive actions

## Error Handling
- Show user-friendly error messages
- Use toast notifications for feedback
- Handle network errors gracefully
- Validate data before submission